summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Blewett Street from Woodlawn Avenue to right of way of N. P. Ry et al, in the City of Seattle, by grading & curbing under Ordinance No. 15108, creating Local Improvement District No. 1378 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
